Traditional Chinese blue-green landscape style, new Chinese fantasy illustration, {argument name="scene" default="moonlit fairyland"}, vertical composition;

Layered peaks of blue-green mountains, the mountain bodies showing a gemstone-like transparent and glowing texture, blue-green gradient, mountain edges with delicate gold leaf outlines and gold embellishments, mountains surrounded by clouds and mist;

In the distance, a giant bright full moon hangs high in the sky, moonlight spilling over the mountains and rivers;

In the foreground, an exquisite classical Chinese pavilion with warm light glowing inside, surrounded by vigorous pine trees, golden trees, streams, waterfalls, mist, and glowing particles, with a river winding through the valley;

In the upper left corner, add vertical handwritten calligraphy characters: {argument name="calligraphy text" default="Oriental Aesthetics"}, with appropriate font size and spacing;

Rich layers, elegant use of white space, ethereal and quiet, dreamy and beautiful, heavy color gongbi style, exquisite details, soft lighting, cinematic atmosphere, high-end national style illustration, ultra-fine, 8K, strong artistic sense, poetic wonderland, 9:16 ratio

